Release Notes

The Sesto Sento guys are back, presenting the second chapter in the
successful Afula On compilation series. Sesto Sento without doubt is
considered as one the leading Trance acts in the world.

Afula is the base city of Sesto Sento and many other bright lights, which
have followed their lead, and have contributed greatly the the global and
domestic rising full on scene.

Afula On Vol.2 has been carefully selected and is presenting 9 previously
unreleased tracks thoroughly tested across the globe with enormous success.

With tracks by Aquatica, Sesto Sento, Gataka, Apocalypse, Intergalactic,
Systemic and Flipper who can go wrong Afula On Vol.2 is another exciting
release from Sesto Sento, destined to rock dance floor all over the globe, a
release which is straight forward, hard and soft, achieving totall balance and
excitement.
